              <h4 class="title">Play With me Music</h4>
              <p class="description">The objective for Play With Me Music classes is for caregivers to have positive musical experiences with their infants and children to encourage bonding. Play With Me Music is designed for children 0-5 years old and their Mom, Dad, or other caregivers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0" style="padding: 15px;"><img src="assets/img/icon/Group.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" style="width: 50px;"></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Group Sessions</h4>
              <p class="description">Music Therapy groups can be provided to a facility as a contract service. Examples of facilities that may use Overlymusical music therapy services are Residential Treatment Centers, Older Adult Facilities, Special Education Classrooms in schools, Preschools or groups of individuals who have similar needs.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0" style="padding: 15px;"><img src="assets/img/icon/Hospice.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" style="width: 50px;"></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Hospice Visits</h4>
              <p class="description">We visit our hospice customers and use music to help provide emotional support, pain relief, and a sense of peace. Our sessions are crafted to alleviate anxiety, foster emotional connections, and enhance the quality of life during this tender phase. </p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0" style="padding: 15px;"><img src="assets/img/icon/OneOn.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" style="width: 50px;"></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">One-on-One Sessions</h4>
              <p class="description">Our one-on-on sessions are for clients who want to improve their mental health; and we address anxiety, depression, addictions and more. We also have neurodiverse clients who use music to increase developmental skills such as motor, social, emotional, and communication.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0" style="padding: 15px;"><img src="assets/img/icon/Lesson.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" style="width: 50px;"></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Music Lessons</h4>
              <p class="description">We offer Group Guitar, individual and adaptive music lessons. Adapted Music Lessons for those who would like to take music lessons but because of physical or various learning challenges need a music therapist to adapt to the unique needs of the student.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0" style="padding: 15px;"><img src="assets/img/icon/Summer.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" style="width: 50px;"></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Summer Camps</h4>
              <p class="description">These camps are designed for kids of all ages. Our summer camps feature activites such as Group Singing, Basic music theory, Songwriting, Active music making and Movement.</p>
            </div>
